data.description: A charming , corner lot brick 3 bedroom cape cod with fantastic curb appeal in the historic Horace Mann area! This beauty welcomes you with a large front deck, perfect for starting your day. The living room has a beautiful fireplace, custom window treatments and chandelier lighting. The updated bathroom features a whirlpool tub and the upper floor bedrooms have new carpeting. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances and the large yard has a privacy fence, with an adjacent 2 car garage. This charmer has new roof and windows, central air, and an alarm system. Great location, near shopping, schools, dining and transportation. Schedule a showing today! Seller is motivated!
